{"tid":1201070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人行本月下旬再來港發行人民幣央票","createTime":"2019-06-11T02:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T02:20:56.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bcd2788ec3001bdfa59dbad2716eebd7bb0dbda7","tid":1201070,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:20:56.000Z","msg":"人行上月亦在香港發行人民幣央票，規模200億元人民幣，分為3個月同1年期，利率分別是3%同3.1%。人行完成發行後一周隨即表示，近期將再次在港發行人民幣央票。<br />\n<br />\n市場人士表示，人行一改以往每季度發行離岸央票的頻率，表明在人民幣貶值壓力加大下，通過收緊離岸流動性進一步釋放維穩訊號。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462030-20190611.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462030-20190611.htm&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD2VlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=4b26d16f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462030-20190611.htm&h=2b3c5e9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462030-20190611.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2G78jfO8HoA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2G78jfO8HoA&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD2VlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=33c01ce5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2G78jfO8HoA</a>"}]}